Visualizing missing data

ggplot(data = penguins,
       aes(x = bill_length_mm ,
           y = bill_depth_mm )) +
  geom_miss_point()

gg_miss_upset(penguins)

gg_miss_var(penguins)
## Warning: `guide = FALSE` is deprecated
## ℹ Please use `guide = "none"` instead.

gg_miss_span(penguins,
             var = bill_depth_mm,
             span_every = 10)
